casebody.data:
Certiorari Denied.

(See also Nos. 551 and 581, supra.) No. 507. City of Omaha et al. v. Frank Brothers Footwear, Inc.

Supreme Court of Nebraska. Certio*936rari denied.

Ralph E. Svoboda for petitioners. Charles S. Rhyne filed a brief for the National Institute of Municipal Law Officers, as amicus curiae, supporting the petition. M. James Spitser filed a brief for Best & Co., Inc., as amicus curiae, opposing the petition.
